<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>The letter that you have received from Close Brothers is a generic letter which they send to all customers whose agreements have been cancelled early.<br></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b>We do appreciate that this is a bit confusing but, as per our previous email, </span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">please rest assured that there is nothing further owed by yourself in relation to your Kingsbridge policy</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>